headline: Is There Still Value in J&J After Shares Jumped 44% in 2025?
summary: Wondering if Johnson & Johnson stock is a hidden gem or already fully priced? This article will break down everything you need to know about its current value. The share price recently moved up by 11.2% over the last month, contributing to a strong 44.1% year-to-date return and a 38.0% gain over the past year.
